				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You are doing the things correctly, and it's very strange you've got the error. According to the text of the error (``Access denied ...''), you don't have rights to create table in the database. I don't know why.
<br />

<br />
I recommend the following: write to the hoster's support and ask to execute the following SQL commands for your account:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
